pageProduct.name: U by Kotex Designer Series Liners Protect 30 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

U by Kotex® Designer Protect liners. Available in a variety of colourful designs and designed for backup protection. Every now and then, we can all do with a little backup, whether it's pre or post period or simply a 'just in case' precaution with tampons. With Designer Protect Liners, you'll be covered anytime of the month!

  • With double all-round protective channels to help prevent bunching
  • With absorbent core to help keep you feeling fresh and dry
  • Breathable backing: allows air to circulate so your skin breathes naturally
  • Soft-touch: cotton-like cover with fun printed designs!
  • Perfect for back up protection to keep you covered

 

With Protect Liners, you'll be covered anytime of the month!

Boxed Contents: 30 Liners

Size: 30 Pack

Directions

Do not flush
